OL,3,C'Your selfishness killed man son':
OL,4,CDad's anger at drink driver
OL,6,FA father whose only son was killed by
OL,7,Fa drunk driver says the image of him
OL,8,Fin his coffin will never leave him.
OL,10,FAdam Cunliffe, 21, was killed
OL,11,Finstantly when he was hit by Paul
OL,12,FWhitfield who was driving his Madza
OL,13,Ftwo-and-a-half times the legal drink-
OL,14,Fdrive limit.
OL,16,FHe then dragged Mr Cunliffe's body
OL,17,Funder his car for 1,000m in front of
OL,18,Fhorrified onlookers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
