OL,3,C'Your selfishness killed man son':
OL,4,CDad's anger at drink driver
OL,6,FWhitfield, 54, was jailed for seven
OL,7,Fyears and four months for causing the
OL,8,Fdeath of the University of Manchester
OL,9,Fanimal technician, who had a young
OL,10,Fson, in St Helens, Merseyside, on 12
OL,11,FJanuary 2022.
OL,13,FHis father Alan Cunliffe, whose victim
OL,14,Fimpact statement was read to Liverpool
OL,15,FCrown Court, said his brave face
OL,16,F"masks the true reality" of his
OL,17,Fdepression since his son's death.
OL,19,FMr Cunliffe Snr said: "I lived and
OL,20,Fbreathed for Adam's existence - he was
OL,21,Fmy only child. My ray of sunshine.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
