OL,3,C'Your selfishness killed man son':
OL,4,CDad's anger at drink driver
OL,6,F"The image of him lying in his coffin
OL,7,Fwith his injuries will never leave my
OL,8,Fmind.
OL,10,FHe said his son's death had forced him
OL,11,Faway from his home in Haydock because
OL,12,Fhe "felt suffocated".
OL,14,FAddressing Whitfield, Mr Cunliffe Snr
OL,15,Fadded: "Your selfishness killed my
OL,16,Fson."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
