OL,3,C'Your selfishness killed man son':
OL,4,CDad's anger at drink driver
OL,6,FThe court heard how father and son had
OL,7,Fshared interests in playing table
OL,8,Ftennis and pool, and enjoyed trips to
OL,9,Fthe Lake District and holidays to
OL,10,FPortugal.
OL,12,FLiam Conway, Mr Cunliffe's brother,
OL,13,Fsaid: "Adam was my best friend, I miss
OL,14,Fhim like crazy. The day we lost him
OL,15,Fwas one of the worst of my life.
OL,17,F"That was also the day my mum broke
OL,18,Fand there was no going back. Our mum
OL,19,Fpassed away aged 43 in April 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
