OL,3,C'Your selfishness killed man son':
OL,4,CDad's anger at drink driver
OL,6,F"All he will have are pictures and
OL,7,Fmemories. One day my sweet, innocent,
OL,8,Ffunny little boy will ask questions
OL,9,Fabout his dad and I don't know how I
OL,10,Fwill answer.
OL,12,F"When it happened I was so lost. I
OL,13,Fstill am and if I didn't have my son I
OL,14,Fdon't know if I would have the
OL,15,Fstrength to keep going."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
