OL,3,C'Your selfishness killed man son':
OL,4,CDad's anger at drink driver
OL,6,FMichael Pickavance, prosecuting, told
OL,7,Fthe sentencing hearing: "On January 12
OL,8,F2022 at around 12:33am, a crash
OL,9,Foccurred between the defendant's blue
OL,10,FMazda and Adam Cunliffe on Washway
OL,11,FLane in St Helens.
OL,13,F"Earlier in the afternoon the
OL,14,Fdefendant was caught on CCTV driving
OL,15,Fhis car into the town centre.J"He
OL,16,Fparked before visiting a number of
OL,17,Fpubs before he ended up at Penny's bar
OL,18,Fon Duke Street.
OL,20,F"While he was getting into his car,
OL,21,FAdam Cunliffe was at the Texaco garage.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
