OL,3,C'Your selfishness killed man son':
OL,4,CDad's anger at drink driver
OL,6,F"An eyewitness, Matthew Rivers,
OL,7,Frecalled Mr Cunliffe was struggling to
OL,8,Fget his words out. He was seen walking
OL,9,Faway down the road."
OL,11,FMr Pickavance told the court that
OL,12,Fshortly after Mr Cunliffe left the
OL,13,Fgarage, an eyewitness - a driver on
OL,14,Fthe opposite carriageway - recalled
OL,15,Fseeing an object lying in the road.
OL,17,FAs they got closer they saw it was a
OL,18,Fperson.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
