OL,3,C'Your selfishness killed man son':
OL,4,CDad's anger at drink driver
OL,6,FDespite the warnings of other
OL,7,Fmotorists who flashed their lights and
OL,8,Fshouted out of their windows, the
OL,9,Fdefendant "neither slowed nor braked
OL,10,Fand drove over Mr Cunliffe".
OL,12,FThe court heard by chance an unmarked
OL,13,Fpolice car was in the area at the time
OL,14,Fand managed to capture Whitfield's
OL,15,Fnumber plate.
OL,17,FThe defendant was arrested at his home
OL,18,Fshortly after 4am and blew 49mcg of
OL,19,Falcohol in 100ml of breath.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
