OL,3,C'Your selfishness killed man son':
OL,4,CDad's anger at drink driver
OL,6,FHowever, Mr Pickavance said analysis
OL,7,Festimated the defendant would have had
OL,8,Faround 86mcg of alcohol in 100ml of
OL,9,Fbreath at the time of the crash. The
OL,10,Flegal limit is 35mcg.
OL,12,FWhitfield, of Hammond Street, St
OL,13,FHelens, pleaded guilty to causing
OL,14,Fdeath by dangerous driving last month.
OL,16,FAddressing Whitfield, Judge Menary
OL,17,Fsaid: "Such was your compromised
OL,18,Fability, you didn't notice motorists
OL,19,Fflashing their lights at you.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
